  * Add 00upstream_gtk3_fixes.patch: Adjust gtk3widgets.py to work with
    current pygobject/gtk. Taken from upstream branch r563.

 -- Martin Pitt <martin.pitt@ubuntu.com>  Fri, 28 Jan 2011 15:45:29 +0100

